;††††††††††††††††††††††††††††††††††††õ;õ;PRINTF.ACT - an highly advanced im-õ;provement of the Library PrintFõ;õ;Copyright (c) 1984 OSS,Inc. and Mark Roseõ;††††††††††††††††††††††††††††††††††††õõ;************************************õ;Internal ToLower functionõ;************************************õõBYTE FUNC PF_ToLower(BYTE c)õõ  IF (c>='A) AND (c<='Z) THENõ    c==+32õ  FIõRETURN(c)õõ;************************************õ;Internal IsDigit functionõ;************************************õõBYTE FUNC PF_IsDigit( BYTE c )õõ  IF (c>='0) AND (c<='9) THENõ    RETURN(1)õ  FIõRETURN(0)õõ;************************************õ;************************************õ õCARD FUNC PF_Nbase(CARD n,base  BYTE ARRAY s)õõ  BYTE length,ptr,dõõ  IF n=0 THENõ    s(1)='0õ    s(0)=1õ    RETURN(s)õ  FIõ  length=0õ  ptr=17õ  WHILE n>0õ    DOõ    d=n MOD baseõ    IF d<10 THENõ      d==+'0õ    ELSEõ      d==+55õ    FIõ    s(ptr)=dõ    ptr==-1õ    length==+1õ    n=n/baseõ    ODõ  s(ptr)=lengthõRETURN(s+ptr)õõ;************************************õ;PrintF to a channelõ;************************************õõPROC PrintFD(BYTE chan  BYTE ARRAY controlõ             CARD c1,c2,c3,c4,c5,c6)õ  BYTE cptr,c,rjustify,õ       zerofill,k,slen,widthõõ  INT prcisnõõ  BYTE POINTER psõõ  INT POINTER argsõõ  BYTE ARRAY s(18)õõ  args=@c1õ  cptr=1õ  DOõ    IF cptr>control(0) THENõ      EXITõ    FIõ    c=control(cptr)õ    cptr==+1õ    IF c='% THEN     ; format character foundõ      ; check for optionsõ      c=control(cptr)õ      IF c='- THENõ        rjustify=0õ        cptr==+1õ        c=control(cptr)õ      ELSEõ        rjustify=1õ      FIõ      IF c='0 THENõ        zerofill=1õ      ELSEõ        zerofill=0õ      FIõ      width=0õ      DOõ        c=PF_ToLower(control(cptr))õ        cptr==+1õ        IF PF_IsDigit(c)=0 THENõ          EXITõ        FIõ        width=10*width+c-'0õ      ODõ      IF c#'. THENõ        prcisn=32767õ      ELSEõ        prcisn=0õ        DOõ          c=PF_ToLower(control(cptr))õ          cptr==+1õ          IF PF_IsDigit(c)=0 THENõ            EXITõ          FIõ          prcisn=10*prcisn+c-'0õ        ODõ      FIõ      ; process conversion charsõ      c=PF_ToLower(c)õ      IF (c='d) OR (c='i) THENõ        IF args^<0 THENõ          ps=PF_Nbase(-args^,10,s)õ          args==+2õ          ps==-1õ          ps(0)=ps(1)+1õ          ps(1)='-õ        ELSEõ          ps=PF_Nbase(args^,10,s)õ          args==+2õ        FIõ      ELSEIF c='u THENõ        ps=PF_Nbase(args^,10,s)õ        args==+2õ      ELSEIF (c='x) OR (c='h) THENõ        ps=PF_Nbase(args^,16,s)õ        args==+2õ      ELSEIF c='o THENõ        ps=PF_Nbase(args^,8,s)õ        args==+2õ      ELSEIF c='b THENõ        ps=PF_Nbase(args^,2,s)õ        args==+2õ      ELSEIF c='s THENõ        ps=args^õ        args==+2õ      ELSEIF c='e THENõ        s(0)=0õ        ps=sõ        PutDE(chan)õ      ELSEõ        IF c='c THENõ          c=args^õ          args==+2õ        FIõ        s(1)=cõ        s(0)=1õ        ps=sõ      FIõ      ; now do filling and print resultõ      slen=ps(0)õ      IF slen>prcisn THENõ        slen=prcisnõ      FIõ      IF rjustify=1 THENõ        WHILE width>slenõ          DOõ          width==-1õ          IF zerofill=1 THENõ            PutD(chan,'0)õ          ELSEõ            PutD(chan,' )õ          FIõ          ODõ      FIõ      k=1õ      WHILE (k<=ps(0)) AND (k<=prcisn)õ        DOõ        PutD(chan,ps(k))õ        k==+1õ        ODõ      IF rjustify=0 THENõ        WHILE width>slenõ          DOõ          PutD(chan,' )õ          width==-1õ          ODõ      FIõ    ELSE     ; not a format stringõ    ; just put out a charõ    PutD(chan,c)õ    FIõ  ODõRETURNõõ;************************************õ;PrintF to default channelõ;************************************õõPROC PrintF(BYTE ARRAY controlõ            CARD c1,c2,c3,c4,c5,c6)õõ  PrintFD(device,control,c1,c2,c3,c4,c5,c6)õRETURNõõ;†ŇÓš†Ôś†–“…ő‘∆ģŃ√‘†õõMODULEõõ